column5: Anyone happen to know what the conditions are like? Is the ice completely gone yet? What are the launch conditions like?
If you don't get any info. soon, PM Curtis.  He lives down that way. Garry
Looked at the sattilite picture and its looking good but I haven't been up to check it out yet.  Heres the link.   http://coastwatch.glerl.noaa.gov/modis/mod...on=o&page=1
